rom the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nWe appreciate your response by 8PM today (2 August 2019).<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=91e150da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"8581f9f8e15848bdcae44de4066e2db5da354a41","tid":1395170,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9083ba5917ec11b58e09fbfe339778126af550","tid":1395170,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}